On the outlying islands , Cheung Chau and Cheung Sha are on Lantau , and Hung Shing Ye and Lo So Shing on Lamma ; inquire about water pollution levels .
Golf .
The Hong Kong Golf Club ( Tel .
2812 7070 ) welcomes visitors to its three 18 - hole courses at Fanling in the New Territories , or the 9 - hole course at Deep Water Bay .
The Discovery Bay Golf Club on Lantau island ( Tel .
2987 7273 ) has an 18 - hole Robert Trent Jones Jr. course , open to visitors Monday, Tuesday , and Friday .
