Jogging .
Victoria Park has a jogging track in Causeway Bay .
Sailing .
Because of the heavy harbor traffic , only sailors licensed by the Hong Kong authorities can run pleasure boats in local waters .
Contact the Hong Kong Yacht Club at Tel .
2832 2817 for information .
Taijiquan ( Tai Chi ) .
